OL,5, Rules on so-called buy now pay later   
OL,6, (BNPL) loans will be tightened up, the 
OL,7, government says - including new        
OL,8, guidelines on advertising and checks to
OL,9, ensure customers can afford to pay.    
OL,11,FApple has said it plans to launch a buy
OL,12,Fnow pay later option for users of Apple
OL,13,FPay, initially in the US.              
OL,15,FBut critics say BNPL schemes encourage 
OL,16,Fpeople to spend beyond their means.    
OL,18,FThe loans - used by 15 million people  
OL,19,Fin the UK in 2021 - are typically      
OL,20,Fspread over a number of payments.      
